title: Chic cubbies to display your cookbooks or serving ware
posting_body: This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 649 Sq.
Located at Fairview and Eastlake, Equinox, just like its name suggests offers the perfect balance of relaxation while still being close to the action.
Being located just minutes from South Lake Union, Downtown, and the University of Washington makes this community the perfect retreat from the city’s hustle and bustle.
Lake Union is also just steps away.
Pack a picnic lunch and head over to Gas Works Park for a fun outing, or reserve our free Paddleboard amenity for a day of fun out on the lake.
Our 24-hour fitness center offers on-demand workouts, spin classes on our Peloton bikes, and tons of free weight and resistance equipment.
Walk to a myriad of different shops and restaurants all located in your new quaint Eastlake neighborhood.
A home at Equinox is the perfect addition to your balanced lifestyle.

Smart-box technology and Cat 5 wiring, Top-of-the-line Viking, Jenn Aire or Fisher & Paykel stainless steel refrigerators*, Chic cubbies to display your cookbooks or serving ware, Stylish ceramic tile surrounds in baths, Ceilings soar from 8'10" up to 16', Rich hardwood flooring throughout*, Custom cabinetry in two different finishes, Polished slab granite kitchen and bathroom countertops, Private balconies or patios*, Viking or Frigidaire gas range and micro-hood, Advanced-technology Frigidaire front loading washer and dryer*, Energy-efficient Bosch stainless steel dishwasher

Dry Cleaning Service, Front Access to Lake Union, Package lockers, 24hr Fitness Center, Business Center, Free Weights, Parking Garage with Full Size Spaces, Peloton Bikes, Reservable Yoga Studio with Fitness on Demand, Rooftop Terrace and Clubhouse, 24hr Fitness Center
